title: Lost Mary DM1200 Disposable Vape
description: Explore the Lost Mary DM1200 Disposable Vape, previously known as the Lost Mary DM600 X2 Disposable Vape . The Lost Mary DM1200 is the new disposable vape brought to you by Lost Mary , similar in style and shape to their original Lost Mary, the Lost Mary BM600 . The Lost Mary DM1200 is a new type of disposable vape that comes with 2 prefilled pods ; each pod has been prefilled with 2ml of 20mg strength nicotine salt vape juice which allows the Lost Mary DM1200 vape to last for up to 1200 puffs overall, as each pod can provide you with up to 600 puffs before it needs to be disposed of. This way the Lost Mary DM1200 disposables can provide you with the same amount of puffs as one of the big puffs vapes remain completely legal within the UK due to their TPD compliance ! Another great feature of the DM1200 Lost Mary is the new and improved pod design ; each of the Lost Mary DM1200 pods features an innovative new coil , the mesh QUAQ coil - this new coil boosts the flavour of the vape juice immensely, as well as improving the longevity and consistency of the Lost Mary DM1200 vapes. As a result your Lost Mary DM1200 disposable vape pods should finish just as the battery does, allowing you to make the most of the e-liquid within your Lost Mary DM1200 kit. Lost Mary Vapes are well known for their fantastic flavour, but the DM1200 Lost Mary vape takes it a step further , with 20 different flavours for you to pick from, all based on the best Lost Mary flavours from the original Lost Mary range as well as their Lost Mary Nic Salts . You can’t go wrong with the DM1200 Lost Mary vapes as there are simply so many different blends to choose from - take a look at the full list below. Lost Mary DM1200 Flavours With 20 different flavours in the Lost Mary DM1200 Disposable, there’s a type for every individual taste. Lost Mary DM1200 Alpine Ice Lost Mary DM1200 Banana Ice Lost Mary DM1200 Blue Razz Lemonade Lost Mary DM1200 Blueberry Cloudd Lost Mary DM1200 Blueberry Lost Mary DM1200 Blueberry Sour Raspberry Lost Mary DM1200 Cherry Ice Lost Mary DM1200 Double Apple Lost Mary DM1200 Grape Lost Mary DM1200 Kiwi Passion Fruit Guava Lost Mary DM1200 Lemon Lime Lost Mary DM1200 Maryturbo Lost Mary DM1200 Mix Berries Lost Mary DM1200 Pineapple Ice Lost Mary DM1200 Pineapple Passionfruit Lemon Lost Mary DM1200 Red Cherry Lost Mary DM1200 Strawberry Ice Lost Mary DM1200 Triple Mango Lost Mary DM1200 Watermelon Lost Mary DM1200 Western Tobacco Lost Mary DM1200 Disposable Vape Specs E-Liquid Capacity : 2ml Nicotine Strength : 20mg (2%) Nicotine Type : Nicotine Salts Puff Count : Up to 1200 Puffs Coil : QUAQ Mesh Coil TPD Compliant Suitable for Mouth to Lung vaping Up to 20 Flavours to Choose From Lost Mary DM1200 Disposable Vapes Contain: 1x Lost Mary DM1200 Disposable Vape Device 2x Lost Mary Disposable Pods Note: Due to last minute changes in the Lost Mary branding it's possible you may receive a Lost Mary DM600 X2 Disposable Vape - however it’s exactly the same as the Lost Mary DM1200 Disposables in everything but name. Are Lost Marys going to be banned? Lost Mary disposable vapes will be banned as part of the new regulations brought in by the UK government ; however it’s not the end of the world as we still have a wide variety of alternatives to disposable vapes , which includes the Lost Mary Tappo - a Lost Mary Prefilled Pod Kit that works similarly to the Lost Mary DM1200 but is rechargeable with a selection of Lost Mary disposable pods available for purchase. How long do Lost Marys actually last? The amount of time that Lost Mary vapes last depends on the user ; those that are used to using Mouth to Lung vapes or that vape less frequently will find that their Lost Mary will last longer than those who vape more frequently or take longer, heavier inhales. Mouth to Lung vapers may find that their Lost Mary vapes last for 2 - 3 days, whilst those who are used to using Sub Ohm vapes may only get a day out of their 600 puff Lost Mary vape. What is the most popular Lost Mary? The most popular Lost Mary is the original Lost Mary, the BM600 Lost Mary, with more of their flashship product selling than any of their other product lines - however the best Lost Mary flavour, which is also the most popular Lost Mary Flavour, would be the Blue Razz Lemonade. The Lost Mary Blue Razz Lemonade is available as a Lost Mary Tappo Blue Razz Lemonade as well as in their range of disposable vapes. Is Lost Mary a fake vape? Lost Mary are a legitimate brand of disposable vapes; however there are illicit Lost Mary vapes on the market . If ever you’re in doubt about the authenticity of your Lost Mary disposable we’d recommend that you check the authentication label on the side of the packaging and enter the 18 digit code into the Lost Mary official website in order to verify it. To reduce the risk of purchasing fake Lost Mary vapes make sure that you only purchase your disposable vapes and vaping products from reputable sources such as genuine vape retailers like Grey Haze , as places such as corner stores and markets may not provide you with the real deal.
